#: numpy.random._generator.Generator.standard_normal:43
msgid "Notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../docstring of
#: numpy.random._generator.Generator.standard_normal:44
msgid ""
"For random samples from the normal distribution with mean ``mu`` and "
"standard deviation ``sigma``, use one of::"
